					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This SCP has potential to be unique, but it doesn't play around with the ideas its given. It's extremely short, simple, vague, it feels incomplete, and there's no real narrative tied to it. The somewhat narrative I gained from the article is it just sounds like the SCP is mocking the foundation and that's it.</p> <p>Overall, it has potential but needs more to it than just manipulated texts and long scroll-downs. I recommend to think through your idea more thoroughly. Please go check out <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/how-to-write-an-scp">this guide</a> or <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/ideation">this one</a> to help you.</p> <p>-1</p> 
